column2: SELECT top #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.dered_u,p.dered_g,p.dered_r,p.dered_i,p.dered_z,  s.specobjid, s.class,s.subclass, s.z,g.specObjID , s.specObjID,  g.h_beta_flux, g.oiii_#_flux, g.h_alpha_flux, g.nii_#_flux,  sm.SFR, sm.logMass  from PhotoObjAll AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort AS sm ON s.specObjID=sm.specObjID  JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON s.specObjID = g.specObjID  WHERE   s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.class=&&&
